/p>\n<p><a href=\"https://affinitydemo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6688\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/affinity-ss-compact/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883\" data-orig-size=\"1665,1751\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883?w=285\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883?w=840\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6688\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883\" alt=\"Affinity screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"883\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&amp;h=883 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=143&amp;h=150 143w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=285&amp;h=300 285w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=768&amp;h=808 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=974&amp;h=1024 974w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg 1665w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thomasguillot.com/\">Thomas Guillot</a> designed <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/shoreditch/\"><strong>Shoreditch</strong></a> especially for businesses who want to easily combine multiple panels on any page.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://shoreditchdemo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6685\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/shoreditch-ss/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959\" data-orig-size=\"720,822\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959?w=263\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959?w=720\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-6685\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959\" alt=\"Shoreditch screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"959\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=131&amp;h=150 131w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=263&amp;h=300 263w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for a fresh new blogging-focussed theme? Check out our trio:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A modern blogging theme that shows off gorgeous photography, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/revelar/\"><strong>Revelar</strong></a> is designed by <a href=\"http://mutelife.com/\">Filipe Varela</a> and developed by <a href=\"https://soakingupthelight.wordpress.com/\">Ola Bodera</a>;</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://diaryofawebsite.com/\">Tammie Lister</a>&#8216;s <strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/cols/\">Cols</a></strong> features a minimalist multi-column text display; and</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/lyretail/\">Lyretail</a>,</strong> designed by <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/melchoyce/\">Mel Choyce</a> and developed by Caroline Moore, is a clean single-column theme for personal bloggers with prominent social links in the header.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Take your favorite for a spin today!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://revelardemo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6690\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/revelar-ss-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630\" data-orig-size=\"720,540\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=720\" class=\"imgborder alignnone wp-image-6690\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630\" alt=\"Revelar screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"630\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.file